Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren’t such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don’t hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, you’re the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:01:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they want to change something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Sumptuous meal!\N– Sumptuous meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little thrown off balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s regroup, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m itchy, Elder Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, itchy…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My punches aren’t having\Nany effect whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn’t look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It itches, Elder Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…feels like I’m getting a rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s futile…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– You won't swagger like that for long!\N– You won't swagger like that for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s up with those guys anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re an idiot brat as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it hard, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having to go on a mission\Nwith that failure of a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you, Iruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Mizuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m asking you, please stop\Nthis kind of foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you intending to betray\Nyour comrades from the village again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NYour comrades from the Leaf Village
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with whom you shared\Nboth pleasures and pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand that,\Ncan’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades…huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you are naïve,\Naren’t you…lruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I believe in is power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t think you can shackle me with\Nsuch vague bonds like that of comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will soon get my hands\Non the ultimate power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Orochimaru’s power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’ll teach you a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About how meaningless it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that thing you and the other Leaf guys\Ndescribe as camaraderie or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were an excellent Shinobi despite\Nhaving committed that crime, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t talk so knowingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They’re dodging all my attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka, if you insist so much,\Nwhy don't you show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What degree of feeling\Nyou really have for your comrades…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder whether you’ll really\Nbe able to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! Forget about these guys!\NPursue Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m gonna settle this later\Nwithout fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother, that guy went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all went off, didn’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother, could this be\Na game of hide-and-go-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide-and-go-seek! Hide-and-go-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean we’re “It”?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making us “It” without even deciding\Nby scissors-paper-rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Let's go, Raijin! 					– Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A New Squad!\N                           Two People and a Dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here…lruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It’s 100 years too soon\Nto be arguing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you dilly-dally the situation’s gonna\Nget really troublesome again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, huh, Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t have time to be\Ndealing with these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother, hide-and-go-seek is fun,\Nbut aren’t you getting hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re really something,\Naren’t you, Raijin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave some for your Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you idiot brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh? 					– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m telling you, it’s foolhardy\Nto be fighting these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter…lruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren’t you gonna stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this foolishness, Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out, Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always be aware of\Nan attack from behind…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a Shinobi,\Nisn’t that a basic rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicely done, Iruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always read behind the surface\Nof your enemy’s bluffs…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a Shinobi isn’t that a basic rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Smoke Bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Come on over! Catch us if you can!\N– Come on over! Catch us if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother, they’re increasing!\NThey’re increasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raijin, this must be\Nsuper hide-and-go-seek, don’t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A decoy strategy, huh?\NYou thought it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can buy some time this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now's our chance…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Super, super hide-and-go-seek!\N– Super, super hide-and-go-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are,\Nthere are two Old Lady Tsunades!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re talking about\Nthe idiotic strength, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven’t you come to\Nyour senses yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so obsessed with power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that, if anything,\Nis everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reconsider, Mizuki!\Nlt isn’t too late yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you understand the situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?\NCome on and attack, Iruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re my comrade from\Nthe same village!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I’m tired of that kind of\Nsong and dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover…\Nyou’re my colleagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a member of the same family\Nthat inherited the same Will of Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will of Fire, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, please stop\Nthe foolishness, Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It irks me most when\Nyou say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we’re old acquaintances\NI was gonna kill you quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I’ve decided against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re gonna have some fun…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll give you a taste of how it feels
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be killed slowly by\Nyour so-called comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naruto… How long are you\Nplanning to be like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just a matter of time till\Nthose guys find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide-and-go-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide-and-go-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother,\Nsuper hide-and-go-seek again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m getting bored with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always,\Nyou have no new tricks, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Okay! 					– Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of game is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're going so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see… Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel sick… Elder Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m woozy…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerks…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you’re doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The preparation’s done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it goes!\NYou fatso Herculean brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate… I must concentrate…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop putting on airs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy like you,\Nwho’s weaker than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That’s right, isn’t it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always excelled over\Nanything I did, didn’t you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always being helped by you,\Nwasn’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One year has passed already, hasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not so easy to laugh,\Nhiding your sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your teacher told me that\Nyou are the center of the laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not sad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s an honor for Shinobi\Nto die during their missions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are heroes who protected this village\Nfrom the Demon Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am the child of those heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I’m not sad\Neven though I’m alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These tears are from the happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m always aware that\Nyou are feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of Leaf’s Shinobi\Nhave the “Will of Fire.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Will of Fire”?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means the will to protect the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have\Nthe Will of Fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you and people in this village\Nare all family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka, I wonder if you have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s that over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I heard that Iruka\Nwas depressed these days…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried and came to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody’s…worried about you, Iruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody’s waiting over there.\NCome on and play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all right… Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mizuki that I idolized was kind…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was a guy who was more\Nthoughtful of his friends than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember! Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an idiot, aren’t you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it goes…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel sick…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh? 					– Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother, don’t tell me that you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Raijin… I squashed…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take this…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Give us back our lunch!\N– Give us back our lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He’s done it, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t look like you understand me,\Nso let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real reason I was kind to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it made me happy\Nmore than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see you in your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Iruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re gonna go play soccer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come join us, Iruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Iruka’s okay
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after all those things\Nthat happened to him…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why we need to\Ntry to cheer him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…only him…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody makes a fuss about him
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because of his parents\Ngetting killed by Nine-Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Lord Hokage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…why is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m gonna try to gain the favor\Nof Lord Hokage too…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I heard that Iruka has been\Ndepressed recently so…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treating a guy who’s weaker\Nthan oneself with disdain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the most pleasurable\Nfeeling of all, Iruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren’t that way in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I’ve been telling you…\Nyou’re naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of naiveté leads to fatal mistakes\Non the battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the battleground, it’s all about\Nhow many enemies you can kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you throw a Kunai blindly\Nin a bamboo grove,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all that will happen is that it’ll bounce off\Nand its path will be errant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re gonna take aim…\Nmake it straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t think I’m gonna get fooled twice\Nwith the same bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… I’m at a disadvantage if\Nwe fight in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it’s useless…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the path is going to be errant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then one just needs to calculate\Nthe path of the Kunai when throwing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you’ve finally gotten serious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you’re finally conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined our meal…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t even think\Nwe’re gonna let you leave here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going for his stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going for his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– One, two… 					– One, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Three! 					– Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break,\Nwhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too much of a drag\Nto tell you my name, however…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful support squad\Nassigned to this mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful trio from\Nthe Village Hidden in the Leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re Ino-Shika-Cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crappy news pass us by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you become speechless
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My voice is way too soft
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don’t answer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re crying   Crying alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?   I’m crying too
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Let my lonely scream ring out\Nthrough the night”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll thrash this confused era\Nwith my speed   Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’ll thrash this confused night\Nwith my speed   Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll thrash them with my piercing guitar\Nand my speed   Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sinking world and its evil bastards,\NI’ll kick their butt   Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these guys?!\NThey have super ridiculous strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think they can resist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Possession Jutsu\Nto this extent on sheer power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shikamaru's Jutsu gets broken now,\Nwe'll be in a hairy spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only choice is to\Nsettle this right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yeah! 					– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go!\NThis is our trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode,\N "A New Formation: Ino-Shika-Cho!"
